quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  9,32,yeh chahtay hain ke khuda ke noor ko apne munh se ( phoonk maar kar ) bujha den aur khuda apne noor ko poora kiye baghair rehne ka nahi. agarchay kafiroon ko bura hi lagey
  9,33,wohi to hai jis ne apne paighambar ko hadaayat aur deen haq day kar bheja taakay is ( deen ) ko ( duniya ke ) tamam deeno par ghalib kere. agarchay kafir nakhush hi hon
  9,34,momino! ( ahal kitaab ke ) bohat se aalam aur mashaiykh logon ka maal na-haq khatay aur ( un ko ) raah khuda se roktay hain. aur jo log sona aur chandi jama karte hain aur is ko khuda ke raste mein kharch nahi karte. un ko is din azaab alim ki khabar suna do
  9,35,jis din woh maal dozakh ki aag mein ( khoob ) garamkiya jaye ga. phir is se un ( bakhilon) ki pishanyan aur pehlu aur pithain daghi jayen gi ( aur kaha jaye ga ) ke yeh wohi hai jo tum ne apne liye jamakiya tha so jo tum jama karte they ( ab ) is ka maza chako
  9,36,khuda ke nazdeek mahinay ginti mein ( baara hain yani ) is roz ( se ) ke is ne asmano aur zameen ko pedakiya. kitaab khuda mein ( baras ke ) baara mahinay ( likhay hue ) hain. un mein se chaar mahinay adab ke hain. yahi deen ( ka ) seedha rasta hai. to un ( mahino ) mein ( qtal na-haq se ) apne aap par zulm nah karna. aur tum sab ke sab mushrikon se laro jaisay woh sab ke sab tum se lartay hain. aur jaan rakho ke khuda parhaiz gaaron ke sath hai
